AboutMe:

I'm currently looking for freelance, consulting, and tutoring work. Contact me if you require any of these services.

Also, I'm due to graduate this May, so as of this summer, I will be looking for full-time work in an area either involving statistics or software development. If you're an employer, solicitation is welcome!
